data.name: sqlSelectCommand11.CommandText
data.value: SELECT p.id, p.proj_lot_id, p.change_date, p.lot_status_id, p.sub_status_id, p.purchaser_id, p.price_quoted, p.end_date, p.phone_num, p.username, p.comments, s.Lot_Status, ss.Sub_Status, c.NAME FROM PROJ_LOT_STATUS_HISTORY p left outer join LD_Lot_Status s on s.Lot_Status_ID=p.lot_status_id left outer join LD_Sub_Lot_Status ss on ss.Sub_Status_ID=p.sub_status_id left outer join CUSTOMERS c on c.CUSTOMER_ID=p.purchaser_id WHERE (proj_lot_id = @proj_lot_id)

data.name: sqlUpdateCommand8.CommandText
data.value: UPDATE [PROJ_LOT_STATUS_HISTORY] SET [proj_lot_id] = @proj_lot_id, [change_date] = @change_date, [lot_status_id] = @lot_status_id, [sub_status_id] = @sub_status_id, [purchaser_id] = @purchaser_id, [price_quoted] = @price_quoted, [end_date] = @end_date, [phone_num] = @phone_num, [username] = @username, [comments] = @comments WHERE (([id] = @Original_id) AND ((@IsNull_proj_lot_id = 1 AND [proj_lot_id] IS NULL) OR ([proj_lot_id] = @Original_proj_lot_id)) AND ((@IsNull_change_date = 1 AND [change_date] IS NULL) OR ([change_date] = @Original_change_date)) AND ((@IsNull_lot_status_id = 1 AND [lot_status_id] IS NULL) OR ([lot_status_id] = @Original_lot_status_id)) AND ((@IsNull_sub_status_id = 1 AND [sub_status_id] IS NULL) OR ([sub_status_id] = @Original_sub_status_id)) AND ((@IsNull_purchaser_id = 1 AND [purchaser_id] IS NULL) OR ([purchaser_id] = @Original_purchaser_id)) AND ((@IsNull_price_quoted = 1 AND [price_quoted] IS NULL) OR ([price_quoted] = @Original_price_quoted)) AND ((@IsNull_end_date = 1 AND [end_date] IS NULL) OR ([end_date] = @Original_end_date)) AND ((@IsNull_phone_num = 1 AND [phone_num] IS NULL) OR ([phone_num] = @Original_phone_num)) AND ((@IsNull_username = 1 AND [username] IS NULL) OR ([username] = @Original_username))); SELECT id, proj_lot_id, change_date, lot_status_id, sub_status_id, purchaser_id, price_quoted, end_date, phone_num, username, comments FROM PROJ_LOT_STATUS_HISTORY WHERE (id = @id)

data.name: sqlDeleteCommand8.CommandText
data.value: DELETE FROM [PROJ_LOT_STATUS_HISTORY] WHERE (([id] = @Original_id) AND ((@IsNull_proj_lot_id = 1 AND [proj_lot_id] IS NULL) OR ([proj_lot_id] = @Original_proj_lot_id)) AND ((@IsNull_change_date = 1 AND [change_date] IS NULL) OR ([change_date] = @Original_change_date)) AND ((@IsNull_lot_status_id = 1 AND [lot_status_id] IS NULL) OR ([lot_status_id] = @Original_lot_status_id)) AND ((@IsNull_sub_status_id = 1 AND [sub_status_id] IS NULL) OR ([sub_status_id] = @Original_sub_status_id)) AND ((@IsNull_purchaser_id = 1 AND [purchaser_id] IS NULL) OR ([purchaser_id] = @Original_purchaser_id)) AND ((@IsNull_price_quoted = 1 AND [price_quoted] IS NULL) OR ([price_quoted] = @Original_price_quoted)) AND ((@IsNull_end_date = 1 AND [end_date] IS NULL) OR ([end_date] = @Original_end_date)) AND ((@IsNull_phone_num = 1 AND [phone_num] IS NULL) OR ([phone_num] = @Original_phone_num)) AND ((@IsNull_username = 1 AND [username] IS NULL) OR ([username] = @Original_username)))
